Maintainer: Lucio Palazzo <lucio.palazzo@unina.it>
Description: Generation, estimation and testing of INAR models. The package 
    provides functions for the generation of Integer Autoregressive models with
    different innovations distributions, the estimation of the parameters of the
    models and tests to check for the goodness of fit.
